<div><div><h2>GSK Pharma Q2 profit down 23% to  101 crore</h2></div><div>glaxosmithkline (gsk)pharmaceuticals on monday reported 22.67% fall in standalone net profit to  100.77 crore for the quarter ended 30 september 2018. the company had posted a net profit of  130.32 crore in the year-ago period said in a bse filing. total income of the company stood at  831.13 crore for the reported quarter. it was  845.89 crore in the second quarter of 2017-18. shares of were trading at  1379.30 per scrip on bse down 3.11% from the previous close.</div></div>